=========================================================

When column needs to be updated/modified:

atter table 'table_name'
modify 'column_name ...';

--------
example:
--------

alter table users
modify id int primary key auto_increment;

--------
example: (adding new column and setting it as reference to another table)
--------

alter table users
add gender varchar(10),
add FOREIGN KEY (gender) REFERENCES genders(type);

=========================================================

